Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.92,0:25:57.55,BDSPEC_JPN,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.92,0:25:57.55,BDSPEC_JPN,,0,0,0,,ナツキさんを\N結界の外に逃がします
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.55,0:25:58.18,BDSPEC_JPN,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.18,0:25:59.18,BDSPEC_JPN,,0,0,0,,～♪
